HEADWORD: holding company
<hw>holding company</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Finance)</fld> <def>A
company that controls other independently incorporated companies by
ownership of most or all of their stock, but does not directly control
the daily operations of those companies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

